_text = "I also feel guilty about who did not come on that trip with me. I had a falling out with this friend. I would have invited them on that camping trip in a heartbeat but we weren't friends at the time.\n\nWhich is such an awful thing to say.”We aren't friends anymore”.\n\nAll of my friendships have just sort of fizzled out because I either moved away or we grew into different people. This was the only friendship that ended in a huge fight.\n\nIt was one of those situations that snowballed into a disaster. Sometimes when I look back, I regret not fighting harder for them. I made such stupid mistakes that lead to everything ending like it did. Sometimes I want to write to them and apologize but I worry that might do more damage.\n\nMaybe one day they will discover this art piece in a gallery and somehow end up on this slide.\n\nI just hope they know that I did truly care for them. In fact, I still do care a great deal today."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, CloudsMemory, CloudsMemory, false)
